---
import type { Brand } from '@shared/content-schemas/config';

interface Props { brand: Brand; source?: string; }
const { brand, source } = Astro.props;
const ac = brand.accentColor;
---
<!-- ===== Page Hero ===== -->
<section
  class="ph"
  data-section="FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ph-eyebrow">Funktionen</div>
    <h1 class="ph-h1">Was im Gespräch <em>wirklich wirkt.</em></h1>
    <p class="ph-sub">Fünf Slider, ein Zehn-Jahres-Verlauf, klare Stufen-Prognose, drei Simulationsmodelle, persönliche Ziele und Netzwerk-Visualisierungen. Jede Funktion einzeln nutzbar — zusammen ein Werkzeug für Interessenten-Gespräche und die eigene Downline.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Feature 1 — Slider ===== -->
<section
  class="feature"
  id="slider"
  data-section="Feature 01 Slider"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap feature-row">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="feature-num">01 / FEATURE</div>
      <h2 class="feature-h">Fünf Slider. <em>Sein</em> Plan, nicht deiner.</h2>
      <p class="feature-p">
        Du brauchst keine Folien-Erklärung des Vergütungsplans. Fünf Regler reichen, um ein Gespräch zu drehen — der Interessent oder Partner stellt selbst ein, was er für realistisch hält. Jede Änderung berechnet die Entwicklung über die Zeit sofort neu.
      </p>
      <p class="feature-p feature-p-highlight">
        Auch mit moderaten Werten wird sichtbar, was Kontinuität über Jahre bewirkt. <b>Erwartungen werden geklärt, nicht gepusht</b> — das nimmt dem Gespräch den Druck, sofort liefern zu müssen.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Member pro Jahr</b> — wie viele baut er aktiv mit auf?</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Shopper pro Jahr</b> — die ruhige Basis, die regelmäßig im Shop bestellt.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>IP pro Monat</b> — wie aktiv ist ein typischer Shopper im Schnitt?</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Duplikation</b> — wie viele seiner Member bauen selber Beine auf?</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Fluktuation</b> — ehrliche Reibung, statt mathematischer Märchenwelt.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <div class="visual-bar">
          <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <div class="file">eingaben · live</div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-sliders">
          <div class="v-slider"><div class="v-slider-head"><span class="v-slider-label">Member/Jahr</span><span class="v-slider-val">2</span></div><div class="v-slider-track"><div class="v-slider-fill" style="width:22%"></div><div class="v-slider-thumb" style="left:22%"></div></div><div class="v-slider-scale"><span>0</span><span>10</span></div></div>
          <div class="v-slider"><div class="v-slider-head"><span class="v-slider-label">Shopper/Jahr</span><span class="v-slider-val">3</span></div><div class="v-slider-track"><div class="v-slider-fill" style="width:35%"></div><div class="v-slider-thumb" style="left:35%"></div></div><div class="v-slider-scale"><span>0</span><span>10</span></div></div>
          <div class="v-slider"><div class="v-slider-head"><span class="v-slider-label">IP / Monat</span><span class="v-slider-val">200</span></div><div class="v-slider-track"><div class="v-slider-fill" style="width:50%"></div><div class="v-slider-thumb" style="left:50%"></div></div><div class="v-slider-scale"><span>0</span><span>400</span></div></div>
          <div class="v-slider"><div class="v-slider-head"><span class="v-slider-label">Duplikation</span><span class="v-slider-val">30<sup>%</sup></span></div><div class="v-slider-track"><div class="v-slider-fill" style="width:30%"></div><div class="v-slider-thumb" style="left:30%"></div></div><div class="v-slider-scale"><span>0</span><span>100</span></div></div>
          <div class="v-slider" style="grid-column: span 2;"><div class="v-slider-head"><span class="v-slider-label">Fluktuation</span><span class="v-slider-val">20<sup>%</sup></span></div><div class="v-slider-track"><div class="v-slider-fill" style="width:20%"></div><div class="v-slider-thumb" style="left:20%"></div></div><div class="v-slider-scale"><span>0</span><span>50</span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Feature 2 — Chart ===== -->
<section
  class="feature"
  id="chart"
  data-section="Feature 02 Verlauf"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap feature-row reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="feature-num">02 / FEATURE</div>
      <h2 class="feature-h">10 Jahre auf einer <em>Kurve.</em> Nicht auf 30 Folien.</h2>
      <p class="feature-p">
        Im 1. Jahr passiert wenig. Im 4. wird's spürbar. Ab dem 7. wird's eindrucksvoll. Das ist die Wahrheit jedes Netzwerks — und die einzige Visualisierung, die diese Geschichte ehrlich erzählt, ist der Verlauf.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Jahr-für-Jahr-Verlauf</b> mit interaktivem Tooltip — er sieht den Sprung von Jahr 3 zu Jahr 4 selbst.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Monats- und Jahresansicht</b> — gleiche Zahlen, andere Perspektive. „4.000/Monat" wirkt anders als „48.000/Jahr".</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Live-Update</b> — bewegt er einen Slider, biegt sich die Kurve sofort mit. Keine Ladezeit, keine Submit-Buttons.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <div class="visual-bar">
          <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <div class="file">verlauf · 10 jahre</div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-chart-head">
          <div>
            <div class="v-chart-h-label">Provision · Jahr 10</div>
            <div class="v-chart-h-num"><span class="cur">€</span>8.420</div>
          </div>
          <div class="v-chart-tabs">
            <div class="v-chart-tab active">/Monat</div>
            <div class="v-chart-tab">/Jahr</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-chart-body">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 500 220" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="chart-grad" x1="0" x2="0" y1="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color={ac} stop-opacity="0.18"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color={ac} stop-opacity="0"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <line x1="25" y1="40" x2="490" y2="40" stroke="#EEF1EF" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="90" x2="490" y2="90" stroke="#EEF1EF" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="140" x2="490" y2="140" stroke="#EEF1EF" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="190" x2="490" y2="190" stroke="#E1E5E2" stroke-width="0.5"/>
            <text x="20" y="44" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">10k</text>
            <text x="20" y="94" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">7k</text>
            <text x="20" y="144" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">4k</text>
            <text x="20" y="194" text-anchor="end" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">€0</text>
            <path d="M 50 188 L 100 184 L 150 174 L 200 158 L 250 138 L 300 112 L 350 84 L 400 56 L 450 36 L 480 26 L 480 200 L 50 200 Z" fill="url(#chart-grad)"/>
            <path d="M 50 188 L 100 184 L 150 174 L 200 158 L 250 138 L 300 112 L 350 84 L 400 56 L 450 36 L 480 26" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="188" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="100" cy="184" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="150" cy="174" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="200" cy="158" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="250" cy="138" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="300" cy="112" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="350" cy="84" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="400" cy="56" r="3" fill={ac}/><circle cx="450" cy="36" r="3" fill={ac}/>
            <circle cx="480" cy="26" r="6" fill={ac} stroke="white" stroke-width="3"/>
            <line x1="350" y1="84" x2="350" y2="200" stroke={ac} stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" opacity="0.4"/>
            <circle cx="350" cy="84" r="6" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4"/>
            <text x="50" y="212" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">J1</text>
            <text x="200" y="212" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">J4</text>
            <text x="350" y="212" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">J7</text>
            <text x="480" y="212" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#7A8983">J10</text>
          </svg>
          <div class="v-chart-tooltip" style="left: 56%; top: 12%">
            <div class="label">Jahr 7 · /Monat</div>
            <div class="val">€3.180</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Feature 3 — Rank Ladder ===== -->
<section
  class="feature"
  id="ranks"
  data-section="Feature 03 Stufen-Prognose"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap feature-row">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="feature-num">03 / FEATURE</div>
      <h2 class="feature-h">Vom Believer zum <em>Diamond.</em> Und wann?</h2>
      <p class="feature-p">
        Der Vergütungsplan kennt klare Stufen — vom <b>Believer</b> über <b>Builder</b>, <b>Bronze</b>, <b>Silver</b>, <b>Gold</b> bis hin zum <b>Diamond</b> und darüber hinaus. {brand.siteName} zeigt nicht nur, ob er aufsteigt, sondern in welchem Jahr — basierend auf seinen eigenen Werten.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Erreichte Stufen markiert</b> — er sieht sofort, wie weit sein Szenario trägt.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Jahresangabe pro Stufe</b> — kein Wischi-Waschi, sondern eine konkrete Wegmarke.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>AV, QGV und QL transparent</b> — er sieht, welche Voraussetzungen wann erfüllt sind.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <div class="visual-bar">
          <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <div class="file">stufen · aufstiegsprognose</div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-kpi-row">
          <div class="v-kpi">
            <div class="v-kpi-label">Netzwerk · Jahr 10</div>
            <div class="v-kpi-val">412</div>
            <div class="v-kpi-delta">↑ aus 2 Member direkt</div>
          </div>
          <div class="v-kpi">
            <div class="v-kpi-label">Höchste Stufe</div>
            <div class="v-kpi-val">Gold</div>
            <div class="v-kpi-delta">erreicht in Jahr 6</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-rank">
          <div class="v-rank-head"><span class="v-rank-title">Aufstieg über 10 Jahre</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row achieved"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Believer</span><span class="v-rank-meta">40 IP · 500 QGV · 3 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">J1</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row achieved"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Builder</span><span class="v-rank-meta">40 IP · 1.500 QGV · 3 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">J2</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row achieved"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Bronze</span><span class="v-rank-meta">100 IP · 3.000 QGV · 3 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">J3</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row achieved"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Silver</span><span class="v-rank-meta">100 IP · 6.000 QGV · 6 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">J5</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row achieved"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Gold</span><span class="v-rank-meta">150 IP · 9.000 QGV · 9 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">J6</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">Diamond</span><span class="v-rank-meta">150 IP · 15.000 QGV · 12 QL</span><span class="v-rank-year">—</span></div>
          <div class="v-rank-row"><span class="v-rank-dot"></span><span class="v-rank-name">1*–3* Diamond</span><span class="v-rank-meta">+ Star-Beine in der Upline</span><span class="v-rank-year">—</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Feature 4 — Drei Simulationsmodelle ===== -->
<section
  class="feature"
  id="modelle"
  data-section="Feature 04 Simulationsmodelle"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap feature-row reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="feature-num">04 / FEATURE</div>
      <h2 class="feature-h">Drei Modelle. <em>Vom einfachen Wachstum bis zur realen Team-Dynamik.</em></h2>
      <p class="feature-p">
        Nicht jedes Team wächst gleich. Ein einfaches Modell hilft beim Einstieg, realistischere Modelle zeigen Streuung und Dynamik. Starte einfach und schalte bei Bedarf mehr Realität hinzu.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Standard</b> — alle Teams wachsen gleichmäßig. Klare Einstiegs-Sicht für das erste Gespräch.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Zufallsverteilung</b> — zufällige Dynamik zwischen Teams. Zeigt Bandbreite statt Durchschnitt.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Momentum</b> — realitätsnah: einzelne Beine entwickeln Dynamik, andere bleiben kleiner. Spiegelt echte Team-Erfahrung.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <div class="visual-bar">
          <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <div class="file">modelle · vergleich</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px;">
          <div style="background: var(--paper-2); padding: 16px 14px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <div style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500;">Standard</div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 70" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width: 100%; height: 60px;">
              <path d="M 5 60 L 25 50 L 50 35 L 75 18 L 95 6" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M 5 62 L 25 52 L 50 37 L 75 20 L 95 8" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
              <path d="M 5 64 L 25 54 L 50 39 L 75 22 L 95 10" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
            </svg>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Gleichmäßig — alle Beine im Gleichschritt.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="background: var(--paper-2); padding: 16px 14px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <div style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500;">Zufall</div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 70" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width: 100%; height: 60px;">
              <path d="M 5 62 L 25 45 L 50 38 L 75 22 L 95 8" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M 5 64 L 25 58 L 50 42 L 75 35 L 95 18" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
              <path d="M 5 60 L 25 55 L 50 30 L 75 28 L 95 12" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
            </svg>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Streuung — Bandbreite statt Durchschnitt.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="background: var(--paper-2); padding: 16px 14px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <div style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500;">Momentum</div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 70" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width: 100%; height: 60px;">
              <path d="M 5 62 L 25 48 L 50 28 L 75 12 L 95 2" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M 5 64 L 25 58 L 50 48 L 75 38 L 95 28" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55"/>
              <path d="M 5 66 L 25 63 L 50 60 L 75 58 L 95 52" fill="none" stroke={ac} stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.35"/>
            </svg>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Stärkere und schwächere Beine.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== Feature 5 — Ziele-Leiter ===== -->
<section
  class="feature"
  id="ziele"
  data-section="Feature 05 Ziele-Leiter"
  data-component-file="shared/components/sections/FeaturesPageDefault.astro"
  data-source={source}
>
  <div class="wrap feature-row">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="feature-num">05 / FEATURE</div>
      <h2 class="feature-h">Ziele-Leiter. <em>Zwischenziele</em> statt nur Endsumme.</h2>
      <p class="feature-p">
        Für Motivation sind Endzahlen oft zu weit weg. Statt nur auf Jahr 10 zu schauen, zeigt die Ziele-Leiter konkrete Zwischenziele im Verlauf — und in welchem Jahr sie nach den eigenen Annahmen erreicht werden.
      </p>
      <p class="feature-p feature-p-highlight">
        Für bestehende Partner ist das oft entscheidender als die Endzahl: <b>Wegmarken machen Fortschritt greifbar</b>, gerade in den ersten Jahren, in denen die Provision noch klein wirkt.
      </p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Produktkosten refinanziert</b> — der erste, leicht erreichbare Anker.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Auto finanziert</b> — Zwischenziel mit greifbarer Wirkung im Alltag.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Mietfrei wohnen</b> — Wegmarke, an der viele Partner durchhalten.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Vollwertiges Einkommen</b> — der Punkt, an dem aus Nebenher ein echtes Standbein wird.</span></li>
        <li><span class="marker"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span><b>Eigene, frei definierte Ziele</b> — was immer den Sponsor oder Partner motiviert.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <div class="visual-bar">
          <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <div class="file">ziele · persönliche wegmarken</div>
        </div>
        <div class="v-rank">
